<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>Samir技术分享博客</title><link>https://SamirLong.github.io</link><description>分享技术，爱折腾</description><copyright>Samir技术分享博客</copyright><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><image><url>https://p3-pc-sign.douyinpic.com/aweme-avatar/tos-cn-i-0813c001_o0AfmjEgNnAFHEDODO9c58fXAtDVACAIhA2m9w~tplv-8yspqt5zfm-300x300.webp?lk3s=93de098e&amp;x-expires=1776236400&amp;x-signature=RFrCBkAdXSae18qyUt5TnMj0Yek%3D&amp;from=2480802190&amp;s=profile&amp;se=false&amp;sc=avatar&amp;l=202604131533453E392785EC1E9BDE19E3</url><title>avatar</title><link>https://SamirLong.github.io</link></image><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 10:59:06 +0000</lastBuildDate><managingEditor>Samir技术分享博客</managingEditor><ttl>60</ttl><webMaster>Samir技术分享博客</webMaster><item><title>如何获取移动光猫管理员密码以及改桥接模式</title><link>https://SamirLong.github.io/post/ru-he-huo-qu-yi-dong-guang-mao-guan-li-yuan-mi-ma-yi-ji-gai-qiao-jie-mo-shi.html</link><description># 1.先用普通用户登录
浏览器输入`192.168.1.1`
输入光猫背面的账号密码
然后新建一个窗口访问`http://192.168.1.1/webcmcc/telnet.html`
会显示open telnet success!

&lt;img width='443' height='144' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/23802456-a38b-4130-8c1a-7bb09d889b7e' /&gt;

# 2.用命令进入telnet
打开控制面板点击程序点击启动或关闭windows
打开telnet确认保存

&lt;img width='413' height='386' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/338ddc06-b701-45b6-b564-f2be324d6553' /&gt;

win+r输入cmd打开命令行
输入`telnet 192.168.1.1`

&lt;img width='335' height='205' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/08463624-dfdc-4a14-8cbc-3d12f4c95a4d' /&gt;

输入你的光猫背面的账号
再输入密码（密码不显示）

&lt;img width='342' height='209' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/50cc33ea-4c41-4d6f-8a2c-4b754a83c5df' /&gt;

再次输入`cd /config/work`

&lt;img width='338' height='216' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c2a5c049-3c64-4d5b-972f-241516534f2e' /&gt;

再次输入`ls -la`回车之后你会看见有个 lastgood.xml

&lt;img width='678' height='339' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8efa09b6-ee7b-4af8-ba2f-41c62b606be7' /&gt;

输入`vi lastgood.xml`回车
最后输入`/TeleAccountName`就能看到账号和密码了

&lt;img width='596' height='611' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/116e983e-7d12-4761-9575-fb0a30fd5e83' /&gt;

# 3.查询自己的宽带拨号上网的账号密码
下载中国移动app
搜索宽带 找到宽带密码重置
重置密码
记下宽带账号和密码留着备用

# 4.将光猫改桥接模式
进入光猫后台输入管理员账号密码
点击网络-宽带设置
找到 INTERNET_B_VID_41
截图保存参数
将连接模式改成bridge保存即可

&lt;img width='965' height='845' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d7fab785-3586-489a-8a9a-55b47819b993' /&gt;

# 5.如果无法修改则需要新建一个（可以修改的话这一步省略）
点击新建
连接模式选择bridge
VLAN ID :保持一致保存即可
然后删除之前的INTERNET_B_VID_41即可
# 6.设置路由器拨号上网
浏览器输入路由器管理地址
点击上网设置
模式选择宽带拨号上网
输入用户名密码即可
。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://SamirLong.github.io/post/ru-he-huo-qu-yi-dong-guang-mao-guan-li-yuan-mi-ma-yi-ji-gai-qiao-jie-mo-shi.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 10:58:34 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>如何获取移动光猫管理员密码以及改桥接模式</title><link>https://SamirLong.github.io/post/ru-he-huo-qu-yi-dong-guang-mao-guan-li-yuan-mi-ma-yi-ji-gai-qiao-jie-mo-shi.html</link><description># 1.先用普通用户登录
